2. the person who's sport is handball is the person drinking tea##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the fan of pop##1
7. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is golf and the fan of r&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | tea      | fanta       | lemonade   |
| Music-Genre      | r&b   | pop  | punk | electronic     |
| Sport      | cricket     | handball | golf        | basketball |

