.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, cranberry, cucumber, mango
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, fishing, gardening
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, lemonade, cola
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person drinking lemonade##2
6. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating cherry and the person eating cucumber##2
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | cucumber | cranberry  | cherry | mango      |
| Hobby   | fishing  | gardening  | baking | collecting |
| Beverage   | cola | iced-tea | water | lemonade     |

