The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, spy, western
4 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, lizard, rabbit
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the person watching crime movies is between the owner of the rabbit and the person who likes blood-red##2
3. the person who likes azure is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
6. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
