2. the person who's hobby is photography is the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the fan of house is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person driving the train##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the fan of salsa and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
