1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsorchid is between the person who growssunflower and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
