.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, garlic, raspberry, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, puzzles, reading
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, swimming, weightlifting, water-polo
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person eating garlic##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person eating strawberry##2
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's sport is swimming##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | strawberry  | raspberry | eggplant | garlic     |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles   | reading  | camping    |
| Sport     | swimming        | water-polo       | rowing      | weightlifting |

