2. the person eating lime is between the person drinking tea and the pakistani##2
3. the italian is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the british is on the far right##1
5. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating lime##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
