.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, jazz, r&b, soul
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, romance, sports
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, horse, mouse
1. the person watching romance movies is the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of pop is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
4. the fan of pop is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the fan of soul##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the fan of jazz and the owner of the cat##2
7. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Music-Genre      | r&b | pop | jazz     | soul   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | sports        | romance  | epic  |
| Pet           | cat      | mouse         | hedgehog | horse |

