4. the owner of the goat is the librarian##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the owner of the goat##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the owner of the goat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
